[
  {
    "startTime": 0.767,
    "endTime": 5.0,
    "text": "Now I thought I'd share some of my favorite worst-advice-ever stories from you guys. Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "This first one is from @RoeyCustard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "-Mmm! -She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "I dropped my brand-new phone in water. My dad said to \"just put it in the microwave for a few seconds.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.0,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "I had to buy a new phone, he had to buy a new microwave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.0,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "That's not good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "This one is from @MrPibb4life. He says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "I once drank a beer bong full of Jägermeister while sitting in a hot tub because my buddy said, \"You can't get drunk at sea level.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "Well, that's -- That's not -- That's..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.0,
    "endTime": 35.0,
    "text": "That is not -- That's bad advice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "That's false."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "You know it's not true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "Yeah, the Navy should know that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "It's true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 45.0,
    "text": "This one's from @kinkyturtle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "She says, \"The guy at the hardware store told my friend that turpentine would remove paint from her hair. It did. It also removed her hair.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "What are you cryin' about?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "-The paint's gone. -Technically, it worked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "This one's from @d nnykingsl y. -Ooh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "-Rather. -Rather."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Where's he from?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 67.0,
    "text": "Good day to you, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "-Danny Kingsley. -Danny Kingsley."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 71.0,
    "text": "I don't know if that's how he talks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.0,
    "endTime": 71.604,
    "text": "But Danny Kingsley."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 81.0,
    "text": "He says, \"My dad told me to always fry bacon shirtless so you never get grease strains.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "Third-degree burns all over his stomach."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "-Are those freckles? -No, they're not freckles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "They're scars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 89.355,
    "text": "They're grease scars. That's bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.355,
    "endTime": 93.0,
    "text": "Turpentine will get those out, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.0,
    "endTime": 95.0,
    "text": "Thanks for the advice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.0,
    "endTime": 94.26,
    "text": "You know my doctor -- Dr. Pepper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.26,
    "endTime": 96.196,
    "text": "-Yeah. Dr. Pepper. -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.196,
    "endTime": 100.867,
    "text": "This one's from @canadianlinz. She said, \"I was going for a job interview, and my brother told me to maintain constant eye contact with the interviewer and never blink.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "Tell me about Casual Friday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.0,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "I'm really excited to work here. I'm a people person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "This one's from @To neo71. He says, \"When my wife said, \"Don't get me anything for my birthday,\" my friend told me not to get her anything to prove that I'm a \"good listener.\"\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "No. That's bad advice. That is bad advice, dude."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 133.0,
    "text": "Oh, my goodness. -No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 134.434,
    "text": "This one's from ScrangelaSaurus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.434,
    "endTime": 146.0,
    "text": "She says, \"My friend once told me, \"You should smoke weed before a job interview, so if you show up to work stoned they won't know the difference.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.0,
    "endTime": 149.0,
    "text": "Where do I see myself in five years?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.0,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "Taco Bell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.0,
    "endTime": 154.521,
    "text": "This last one's from @liz nawrocki."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.521,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "She says, \"My doctor told me to \"go to see a real doctor.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 160.0,
    "text": "Oh, wow. That's bad advice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.0,
    "endTime": 161.0,
    "text": "There you have it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "Those are \"Tonight Show Hashtags.\""
  },
  {
